{"TopicId":157552,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Old DOS Shuttle Sim","CreatedByName":"Frednoeyes","CreatedById":160594,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-10T04:34:25Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Frednoeyes","CreatedById":160594,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-10T04:34:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHas anybody heard of this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/Q0xZlCv6CYs?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022http://www.myabandonware.com/media/screenshots/s/shuttle-the-space-flight-simulator-1i7/shuttle-the-space-flight-simulator_1.gif\u0022 src=\u0022http://www.myabandonware.com/media/screenshots/s/shuttle-the-space-flight-simulator-1i7/shuttle-the-space-flight-simulator_1.gif\u0022\u003E\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022http://www.myabandonware.com/media/screenshots/s/shuttle-the-space-flight-simulator-1i7/shuttle-the-space-flight-simulator_2.gif\u0022 src=\u0022http://www.myabandonware.com/media/screenshots/s/shuttle-the-space-flight-simulator-1i7/shuttle-the-space-flight-simulator_2.gif\u0022\u003E\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022http://www.myabandonware.com/media/screenshots/s/shuttle-the-space-flight-simulator-1i7/shuttle-the-space-flight-simulator_4.gif\u0022 src=\u0022http://www.myabandonware.com/media/screenshots/s/shuttle-the-space-flight-simulator-1i7/shuttle-the-space-flight-simulator_4.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s called \u003Cem\u003EShuttle: The Space Flight Simulator\u003C/em\u003E, it was made for DOS in 1992, and I absolutely love it!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThough then again I like a game where you essentially flip switches for an hour or so, then have to land the Shuttle using keyboard controls, so perhaps I\u0027m just mad.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s on abandon-ware sites nowadays, so if you want to you can all have a go yourselves, but if you want the lovely sound as seen in the video, you\u0027ll have to set up a Roland MT-32 sound emulator.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... Just thought I\u0027d share what I think is a cool old game that nobody\u0027s probably heard of.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(video courtesy \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC_DzFn0bLaSR_EvaAh8FKZA\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EThriftweeds\u003C/a\u003E)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-03-10T04:36:30Z\u0022 title=\u002203/10/2017 04:36  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 10, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Frednoeyes\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"razark","CreatedById":32993,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-10T06:15:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222981425\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157552\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221489120465\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160594\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Frednoeyes\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Frednoeyes said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHas anybody heard of this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I had it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStill do, on DOSBox.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerbMav","CreatedById":70338,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-10T06:50:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGreat game. Never managed to play on higher than \u0022commander, please come over here and press this button, sir\u0022 difficulty though. ^^\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut I could draw on the experience during my first ksp EVAs from the satellite capture and MMU missions here. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Harry Rhodan","CreatedById":119953,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-10T10:42:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can play it in your browser on archive.org. There are also a few even lesser known other space games like Orbiter, Project Space Station and E.S.S. Mega: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://archive.org/details/softwarelibrary_msdos_games?\u0026amp;sort=-downloads\u0026amp;and%5B%5D=shuttle\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://archive.org/details/softwarelibrary_msdos_games?\u0026amp;sort=-downloads\u0026amp;and[]=shuttle\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Frednoeyes","CreatedById":160594,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-10T15:52:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222981483\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157552\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221489128613\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002270338\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KerbMav\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, KerbMav said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGreat game. Never managed to play on higher than \u0022commander, please come over here and press this button, sir\u0022 difficulty though. ^^\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut I could draw on the experience during my first ksp EVAs from the satellite capture and MMU missions here. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHeh, same here.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Camacha","CreatedById":59088,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-10T22:16:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe dithering is real. Oh, the dithering!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf I did not know better, I would have said this is something recent that was made to look old. I guess the original makers should take that as a compliment.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}